“Mrs. James Cormier died April 19, 1956 at Saint John Hospital.  She was the former Alda Maude Glendenning born in Canobie May 2, 1883.  She was the daughter of Walter and Elizabeth Glendenning.  She is survived by her husband and four daughters Mrs. George Hood (Edna) in Lewiston, Maine;  Mrs. Fred Bierley (Doris) in Long Island, NY;   Mrs. Clayton Scott (Lillian) in Bathurst Mines;

